spirit:hwParameter.spirit:prompt: No. of multi-frames in ILA sequence:
No. of control words per frame clock period per link (CF):
No. of control bits per sample (CS):
Total no. of bits per sample (N'):
No. of samples per converter per frame cycle (S):

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:script: Enable('ECC_ENABLE', And(Neq('FAMILY', 'SmartFusion2'), Neq('FAMILY', 'IGLOO2')));\ Validate('Maximum size of a multi-frame is 1024 octets. Please change the value of F and/or K to reduce number of octets in a multi-frame.', Less(Mul('F', 'K'), '1025'));\ Validate('Minimum size of a multi-frame is 17 octets. Please change the value of F and/or K to increase number of octets in a multi-frame.', Gt(Mul('F', 'K'), '16'));\ Validate('In FPGA Fabric RAM selection should only be used for F*K < 21', Or(And(Eq('RAM_SEL', 'In FPGA Fabric'), Less(Mul('F', 'K'), '21')), Neq('RAM_SEL', 'In FPGA Fabric')));\ Validate('PolarFire uSRAM does not support ECC', Or(Eq('ECC_ENABLE', '0'), Neq('FAMILY', 'PolarFire'), Neq('RAM_SEL', 'In uSRAM')));\ Validate('PolarFireSoC uSRAM does not support ECC', Or(Eq('ECC_ENABLE', '0'), Neq('FAMILY', 'PolarFireSoC'), Neq('RAM_SEL', 'In uSRAM')));\ Validate('In FPGA Fabric RAM does not support ECC', Or(Eq('ECC_ENABLE', '0'), Neq('RAM_SEL', 'In FPGA Fabric')));\

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: CoreJESD204BRX is the receiver interface of the JEDEC JESD204B standard. This specification describes a high speed serial interface for data converters
